{"pageid":53903,"pagename":"Lesser magical balance","title":"Lesser magical balance","displaytitle":"Lesser magical balance","revid":14249552,"redirects":["Elemental balance 1","Lesser Magical Balance","Magical balance 1"],"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Lesser_magical_balance_built.png"},{"name":"description","value":"A lesser magical balance can be built in the Elemental balance space of the Games room in a player-owned house. It requires 37 Construction to build and when built, it gives 176 experience. The player must have a hammer and a saw in their inventory to build it."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile navigation-not-searchable rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Lesser magical balance.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Lesser_magical_balance\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Lesser magical balance\">rsw:Lesser magical balance</a></span></div>\n<table class=\"infobox no-parenthesis-style\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-header\">Lesser magical balance</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-image infobox-full-width-content\"><a href=\"/w/File:Lesser_magical_balance_built.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Lesser magical balance built.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Lesser_magical_balance_built.png/280px-Lesser_magical_balance_built.png?893ba\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"280\" height=\"233\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Lesser_magical_balance_built.png/420px-Lesser_magical_balance_built.png?893ba 1.5x, /images/thumb/Lesser_magical_balance_built.png/560px-Lesser_magical_balance_built.png?893ba 2x\" data-file-width=\"1755\" data-file-height=\"1459\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\">Icon</th><td colspan=\"13\"><a href=\"/w/File:Lesser_magical_balance_icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Lesser magical balance icon.png\" src=\"/images/Lesser_magical_balance_icon.png?dd336\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"15\" height=\"14\" data-file-width=\"15\" data-file-height=\"14\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\">Furniture name</th><td colspan=\"13\">Elemental balance</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\">Released</th><td colspan=\"13\"><a href=\"/w/31_May\" title=\"31 May\">31 May</a> <a href=\"/w/2006\" title=\"2006\">2006</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:PLAYER-OWNED_HOUSES!\" title=\"Update:PLAYER-OWNED HOUSES!\">Update</a>)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Construction\" title=\"Construction\">Level</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">37</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Experience\" title=\"Experience\">Experience</a></th><td colspan=\"13\"><span class=\"infobox-quantity\" data-val-each=\"176\"><span class=\"infobox-quantity-replace\">176</span> xp</span></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\">Room</th><td colspan=\"13\"><a href=\"/w/Games_room\" title=\"Games room\">Games room</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Hotspot\" title=\"Hotspot\">Hotspot</a></th><td colspan=\"13\"><a href=\"/w/Elemental_balance_space\" title=\"Elemental balance space\">Elemental balance space</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Flatpack\" title=\"Flatpack\">Flatpackable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\">Examine</th><td colspan=\"13\">You can practice your magic here.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"7\">Object ID</th><td colspan=\"13\">13395</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"7\">Icon Item ID</th><td colspan=\"13\">8156</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<p>A <b>lesser magical balance</b> can be built in the <a href=\"/w/Elemental_balance_space\" title=\"Elemental balance space\">Elemental balance space</a> of the <a href=\"/w/Games_room\" title=\"Games room\">Games room</a> in a <a href=\"/w/Player-owned_house\" title=\"Player-owned house\">player-owned house</a>. It requires 37 <a href=\"/w/Construction\" title=\"Construction\">Construction</a> to build and when built, it gives 176 <a href=\"/w/Experience\" title=\"Experience\">experience</a>. The player must have a <a href=\"/w/Hammer\" title=\"Hammer\">hammer</a> and a <a href=\"/w/Saw\" title=\"Saw\">saw</a> in their inventory to build it.\n</p><p>To play the game, there must be two players. Each player has a turn at turning the sphere to the colour white, which means it has balanced with all of the elements. Using higher-level spells on it, such as <a href=\"/w/Fire_Wave\" title=\"Fire Wave\">Fire Wave</a>, will make the sphere more of the element's colour than a lower-level spell, such as <a href=\"/w/Fire_Strike\" title=\"Fire Strike\">Fire Strike</a>. Using this can help in turning the sphere white. To change the sphere white, you cast the spells that begin to balance it. If it is slightly green, perhaps you should not use any <a href=\"/w/Earth_spells\" title=\"Earth spells\">Earth</a>-based spells.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mechanics\">Mechanics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Lesser_magical_balance?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Mechanics\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Lesser_magical_balance?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Mechanics\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Each element has a colour. Air is cyan, water is blue, earth is green, fire is red. The more of an element there is, the brighter the orb will be. there are 6 levels of brightness. very slight, slight, a bit, quite, bright and glowing bright. air and earth are opposites, as are water and fire. if the ball is cyan, you can reduce its colour by casting the opposite of air, which is earth, and vice versa. the colour of the ball will be represented by which of the two pairs is strongest. A strike spell will change the colour by 1 shade, a bolt by 2, a blast by 3, a wave by 4, and a surge by 5.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Creation\">Creation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Lesser_magical_balance?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Creation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Lesser_magical_balance?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Creation\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"recipe-table\" style=\"width:-moz-fit-content;width:fit-content;\"><table class=\"wikitable align-center-2 align-right-3\" style=\"margin:0;width:100%\"><caption>Requirements</caption><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Skill</th><th>Level</th><th>XP</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Construction\" title=\"Construction\"><img alt=\"Construction\" src=\"/images/thumb/Construction_icon.png/21px-Construction_icon.png?f9bf7\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" srcset=\"/images/Construction_icon.png?f9bf7 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"25\" /></a> <a href=\"/w/Construction\" title=\"Construction\">Construction</a></td><td>37 <sup title=\"This requirement is boostable\" style=\"cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\">(b)</sup></td><td>176</td></tr><tr><th>Members</th><td><div class=\"cen